snippet.title: Breakers Collection | PC, PS4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
#QUByteConnect2020
A cult-classic among the fans of  Fighting Games, Breakers was released in 1996 for the Neo geo and Arcades, with its sequel, Breakers Revenge, following up two years later.
This collection will feature both of the original games and brand new content.


Media Contact:
pr@qubyteinteractive.com

About QUByte Interactive
QUByte Interactive is a Brazilian game developer and publisher focused on delivering high quality experiences across the most diverse platforms, from mobile to PC to Video game consoles, with business partners in several countries such as USA, Canada, Germany, Japan and China.
